
Package: R.devices.rgl
======================

Version: 0.1.2 [2015-02-25]
o ROBUSTNESS: Package now asserts that the installed version of 'rgl'
  is compatible with the current version of 'R.devices.rgl'.


Version: 0.1.1 [2015-02-03]
o Added argument 'class' for injecting a 'class' attribute to the
  HTML canvas generated when RGL device is closed with devOffRGL().
o Added package vignette.


Version: 0.1.0 [2015-01-28]
o Created package.


Version: 0.0.1 [2014-09-02]
o Initial set of functions created.
